snippet.title: Aliens Vs. Predator 2: Primal Hunt (2002) - AvP2 PH - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Aliens versus Predator 2: Primal Hunt is the 2002 expansion pack for the 2001 video game Aliens versus Predator 2. It was developed by Third Law Entertainment and published by Sierra Entertainment and Fox Interactive for the PC. It is a prequel to the main game, primarily taking place on LV-1201 some five weeks before the events of Aliens versus Predator 2, and establishes background for many of the plot points in the latter. Several characters from the main game make a return.
